arts.ttl: St. Pauli celebrate safety despite Boadu's brace
arts.sum: Bochum bow out of Bundesliga with a solid win away at St. Pauli, who avoided relegation for the first time since the 1995/96 season.

arts.ttl: St. Pauli vs. Bochum preview: Hosts look to secure second successive top-flight campaign
arts.sum: St. Pauli enter Saturday's Bundesliga final day needing a point against relegated Bochum to secure their survival in the top flight.
